List allSections=
[{"section":"51099","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Enter details about all the responsibilities you have handled and is worth mentioning in your resume.&nbsp;<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Position of Responsibility","sectionLink":"position-responsibility","sectionTable":"cv-POA","status":"1"},{"section":"51100","main":"1","defaultSection":"1","sectionContent":"<div>Your basic information like your nationality, marital status, etc needs to be entered in this section.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Basic Info","sectionLink":"basic-info","sectionTable":"cv-basic-info","status":"1"},{"section":"51101","main":"1","defaultSection":"1","sectionContent":"<div>Enter your contact details in this section.&nbsp;<\/div><div><br \/>You can leave the &quot;Full Address&quot; section blank if you do not wish to share your complete address.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Disclosing your contact number and email id is however mandatory.&nbsp;<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Contact Details","sectionLink":"contact-info","sectionTable":"cv-contact","status":"1"},{"section":"51102","main":"1","defaultSection":"1","sectionContent":"<div>Upload a High Resolution &quot;Single&quot; Professional photograph of yours which will be the&nbsp;profile image of&nbsp;your resume.&nbsp;<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Remember your photograph will be the first thing your prospective employer will view.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Profile Image","sectionLink":"image","sectionTable":"cv-images","status":"1"},{"section":"51103","main":"1","defaultSection":"1","sectionContent":"<div>Enter a brief description about your career history and the most valuable skills and experience you have to offer.<\/div><div><br \/>It is the first thing a potential employer reads about you, so you can sell yourself quickly by writing a very impressive description.<\/div><div><br \/>The summary should be in a paragraph not&nbsp;having&nbsp;more than 3-5 compact sentences.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Introduction","sectionLink":"introduction","sectionTable":"cv-introduction","status":"1"},{"section":"51104","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Enter your work experince history in this section. This is the most important section of your resume because based on it, your prospective employer will decide&nbsp;upon your candidature.&nbsp;<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>While writing a brief description about your roles and responsibilities, be accurate, concise and use minimum words.&nbsp;<\/div><div><br \/>For example: Rather than &quot;I was responsible to work on a daily basis with the company&#39;s most important clients and helped them solve problems&quot;, write it as &quot;Worked with clients to solve problems&quot;.<br \/><br \/>In this section do not enter details about the Projects you have undertaken in your organization. A seperate section is available to add deatils on&nbsp;Projects.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Work Details","sectionLink":"work-details","sectionTable":"cv-work","status":"1"},{"section":"51105","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Enter details about all the projects you have undertaken in your career&nbsp;which you think are worth mentioning in your resume.&nbsp;<\/div><div><br \/>Remember, details entered in this section shall be a part of the&nbsp;&#39;Work Experience&#39;&nbsp;section of your resume.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Work Projects","sectionLink":"projects","sectionTable":"cv-project","status":"1"},{"section":"51106","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>If you have undergone any internship program, summer program or articleship while pursuing any degree or course, then enter relevant details in this section.&nbsp;<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Internships","sectionLink":"internships","sectionTable":"cv-internship","status":"1"},{"section":"51107","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>In this section, showcase your training skills by entering details about the&nbsp;trainings that you have conducted. Details about trainings conducted both independently and in the course of your job should be disclosed here.&nbsp;<\/div><div><br \/>By giving a brief description about the trainings you have conducted, you can let your prospective employer know about your areas of expertise, your capability in handling a team and your leadership skills.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Trainings Conducted","sectionLink":"training-conducted","sectionTable":"cv-trainings","status":"1"},{"section":"51108","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>If you hold any professional qualification like &quot;MBA&quot;, &quot;Chartered Accountant&quot;, etc, enter details in this section.<\/div><div><br \/>Please do not enter details about any certification or short term courses here, A&nbsp;seperate section is available for disclosing such courses.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Professional Qualifications","sectionLink":"professional-details","sectionTable":"cv-professional","status":"1"},{"section":"51109","main":"1","defaultSection":"1","sectionContent":"<div>Enter details about your Secondary, Higher Secondary and Graduation in these sub sections. These are compulsory sections.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Educational Background","sectionLink":"educational-details","sectionTable":"cv-education","status":"1"},{"section":"51110","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>If you have undertaken any certification courses like &quot;Certificate in Digital Marketing&quot; , &quot;PC Assembly and Troubleshooting Training&quot;, &quot;Advance Certificate in Management&quot;, etc., enter details in this section<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Certificates","sectionLink":"certificates","sectionTable":"cv-certification","status":"1"},{"section":"51111","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Showcase you technical skills by entering details in this section.&nbsp;<br \/>For example: You have &quot;working knowledge about Java&quot; or &quot;expert knowledge about MS Office.&quot;<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Technical Knowledge","sectionLink":"technical-knowledge","sectionTable":"cv-technical","status":"1"},{"section":"51112","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Enter details about your writings that has&nbsp;been published in any journal, magazine, newspaper or has&nbsp;been included in any conference proceedings.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Publications","sectionLink":"publications","sectionTable":"cv-publications","status":"1"},{"section":"51113","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div><span>Enter details about patent that have been granted to you by government authority.&nbsp;<\/span><br \/><span>Invention for which patents have been granted can be a product or a process that provides, in general, a new way of doing something or offers a new technical solution to a problem<\/span><\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Patents","sectionLink":"patents","sectionTable":"cv-patent","status":"1"},{"section":"51114","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Do not mention your job responsibilities under this section, they don&#39;t fall under the category of achievements.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/div><div><br \/>Achievements are things you did and which&nbsp;had a lasting impact for your company or client. It is a result that you personally bring about while fulfilling your roles and responsibilities.&nbsp;<\/div><div><br \/>Your achievements are unique to your experience and tells the employer that you can deliver.&nbsp;<br \/><br \/>Do not add any National\/State level awards received as we have a seperate section for that.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Achievements","sectionLink":"achievements","sectionTable":"cv-achievements","status":"1"},{"section":"51115","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>If you have received any scholarships or honors and awards in your education or work &nbsp;life, enter details in this section.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Honors & Awards","sectionLink":"honors-awards","sectionTable":"cv-awards","status":"1"},{"section":"51116","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>In this section enter details about your associations with professional organisations.&nbsp;<br \/><br \/>For example: &quot;You are a member of The Institute of Company Secretaries of India&quot;, &quot;You are the Secretary of Rotary Wing Society of India&quot;, etc.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Associated Members","sectionLink":"associations","sectionTable":"cv-association","status":"1"},{"section":"51117","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>If you are associated with any NGOs and have volunteered in social activities, enter relevant details here.&nbsp;<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Volunteer Experience","sectionLink":"volunteer-experience","sectionTable":"cv-volunteer","status":"1"},{"section":"51118","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>When completing this section, consider entering skills that has been&nbsp;asked for, by your prospective employer for the job position you&#39;re seeking. Employers quickly scan resumes. So,&nbsp;long lists are not likely to be read.&nbsp;<br \/>Hence a short, targeted skills&#39; list will be more effective than a&nbsp;long and overwhelming one.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Soft Skills","sectionLink":"skills","sectionTable":"cv-skills","status":"1"},{"section":"51119","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Hobbies and interests you put on your resume, say something specific about you to your employers. Therefore,&nbsp;try to mention those interests and hobbies that matches the requirement of the job role.<br \/><br \/>For Example: If you are applying for a trainer&#39;s profile, then mentioning hobbies like, blogging and web browsing might seem irrelevant or insignificant.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Interests","sectionLink":"interests","sectionTable":"cv-interests","status":"1"},{"section":"51120","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Mention here, the languages you can speak, read or write. There is also an option of mentioning a particular language which you can only speak and cannot write. You see, The&nbsp;More, the merrier.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Spoken Languages","sectionLink":"spoken-language","sectionTable":"cv-languages","status":"1"},{"section":"51121","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Enter details about your job preference, notice period, recomendations, etc in this section.&nbsp;<br \/>In case you do not want to add a particular information in your Resume, use the &quot;skip&quot; button to move to the next section.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Preferences","sectionLink":"preferences","sectionTable":"cv-preference","status":"1"},{"section":"51122","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Enter details about all the projects you have researched and presented in your Instititute&nbsp;which you think are worth mentioning in your resume.&nbsp;<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>This section may be irrelavant for those having more than 2&nbsp;years of work experience.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Academic Projects","sectionLink":"academic-projects","sectionTable":"cv-academic-projects","status":"1"},{"section":"51123","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Co-curricular refers to extra activities, programs, and learning experiences other than the educational activities.&nbsp;<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Co-Curricular Activities","sectionLink":"co-curricular-activities","sectionTable":"cv-co-curricular-act","status":"1"},{"section":"51125","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Presentation refers to activities, PPTs, and seminars, that&nbsp;students have presented in their college.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Presentations","sectionLink":"presentations","sectionTable":"cv-presentations","status":"1"},{"section":"51126","main":"1","defaultSection":"0","sectionContent":"<div>Add a section anywhere in your resume.<\/div>","sectionContentApp":"This is the default content for the application to be fetched","sectionName":"Add a Section","sectionLink":"add-section","sectionTable":"cv-add-section","status":"1"}];